metadata.description:
Part 2 of the experimental collection  >>BACK to ANALOG<< jam series - raw formats with minimal edits & maximum vibes. 

This edition "B.00002" was made in my home studio in Brooklyn, NYC on Thursday December 8, 2022 using the following gear:

- Moog DFAM
- Moog Subharmonicon
- Moog One
- Deckards' Dream by Black Corporation
- Arturia Drumbrute Impact

Cover art is a shot I took on my 120 medium format Seagull TLR analog film camera in Marrickville, Sydney, Australia.












*cough*
